### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/health

### List children (root)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/drive/children

### Create folder
POST http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/drive/folder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TestFolder",
  "parent_id": null
}

### Presign upload
POST http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "demo.pdf",
  "mime_type": "application/pdf",
  "folder_id": null
}

### Complete upload (contoh body; ganti id/size/checksum dari hasil presign & upload)
POST http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/uploads/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "REPLACE",
  "size": 12345,
  "checksum": "deadbeef"
}

### Files table (dashboard)
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/files

### Quick search
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/api/drive/search?q=demo
